        date: "February 02, 2024",
        content: "Thalapathy Vijay officially announced the name of his new political party, 'Tamilaga Vettri Kazhagam' (TVK), and its registration with the Election Commission. In his inaugural statement, he declared that the party would be built on the foundations of 'Secular Social Justice, Equality, and Democratic values' to bring about a transformative change in Tamil Nadu.\n\nThis announcement sent shockwaves through the political landscape of the state. He also confirmed that he would transition into full-time politics after completing his current film assignments. 'Our ultimate goal is the 2026 Assembly Elections,' he explicitly stated.",
