        date: "June 28, 2024",
        content: "Addressing a massive student gathering in Thiruvanmiyur, Chennai, Thalapathy Vijay expressed deep concern over the rising drug menace in Tamil Nadu. 'Students must prioritize social welfare alongside their education,' he urged. He declared that creating a drug-free Tamil Nadu is one of the core missions of TVK.\n\nHe also advised the youth not to fall prey to false propaganda and to approach politics with a deep and nuanced understanding. This powerful speech was delivered as part of his state-wide education excellence awards ceremony.",
